The Crystallographic Data Toolkit (CDTK) is a collection of Python
modules for working with crystallographic data on biomolecules.

For more information, see the tutorial (Doc/tutorial.pdf) and the
reference manual (Doc/reference/index.html).

CDTK is distributed under the CeCILL-C licence. See the file
LICENCE (in English) or LICENSE (in French) for the details of this
licence.


